凜子","body":"呵呵，抱歉、抱歉。\n不過，小奈你很拼命呢","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":225,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":225,"voiceId":"event289-01-007","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"麻里奈","body":"這點工作人員們大家都是一樣喔。\n畢竟是CiRCLE跟RiNG一起舉辦的\n室外RockFes啊！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"event289-01-008","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":225}],"windowDisplayName":"凜凜子","body":"說得也是呢！\n畢竟集合了跟『與樂團相遇，與樂團一起在青春中奔馳』\n這個主題非常相襯的樂團嘛","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":225,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":225,"voiceId":"event289-01-009","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"麻里奈","body":"是啊。雖然從開始策畫至今花費了不少時間，\n但也因此徹底做好讓來場的觀眾看得開心的準備了","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"event289-01-010","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"麻里奈",